; Test collapse handle_value with BALANCE/SEQUENCE type
; Exercise the compound value path in handle_value by collapsing same-day xacts

2024/01/01 Test1
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/01 Test2
    Expenses:Food    10 EUR
    Assets:Cash     $-11.00

test reg --collapse Expenses
24-Jan-01 Test1                 Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
24-Jan-01 Test2                 Expenses:Food                10 EUR       $10.00
                                                                          10 EUR
end test
